      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds like a good starting point for the setting. i want to lean into the atmosphere though. when i think about those specific areas, there's always this sense of tension or something lurking in the shadows. can you write a descriptive paragraph describing a walk through one of these streets at night? make it feel really unsettling, maybe hint at why the people living there or passing through might feel on edge or unsafe.",
